msgstr "一种大型爆破弹，尺寸约为.50勃朗宁机枪弹的两倍，重量更是数倍。"

#: .\at_ammo.json
msgid "33x308mm IHEAT"
msgid_plural "33x308mm IHEATs"
msgstr[0] "33x308毫米IHEAT弹"

#. ~ Description for {'str': '33x308mm IHEAT'}
#: .\at_ammo.json
msgid ""
"A large shell with a label near the bottom of the casing; WARNING DO NOT "
"FIRE WITHIN 80FT OF FREINDLY UNITS. this is probably very explosive."
msgstr "一种大型炮弹，弹壳底部附近有标签：警告，不要在80英尺内对友军单位开火。这可能极具爆炸性。"

#: .\at_ammo.json
msgid "65x465mm shell"
msgid_plural "65x465mm shells"
msgstr[0] "65x465毫米炮弹"

#. ~ Description for {'str': '65x465mm shell'}
#: .\at_ammo.json
msgid "A huge shell this and uh yeah this kills shit dead."
msgstr "一种巨型炮弹，嗯，是的，这玩意儿能把东西彻底干掉。"

#: .\at_ammo.json
msgid "65x465mm shell NUCLEAR."
msgid_plural "65x465mm shell NUCLEAR.s"
msgstr[0] "65x465毫米炮弹 核弹头。"

#. ~ Description for {'str': '65x465mm shell NUCLEAR.'}
#: .\at_ammo.json
msgid "A huge shell this and uh yeah this kills shit extra-dead."
msgstr "一种巨型炮弹，嗯，是的，这玩意儿能把东西炸得连渣都不剩。"

