#: .\at_armor.json
msgid "advanced power armor"
msgid_plural "advanced power armors"
msgstr[0] "先进动力装甲"

#. ~ Use action holster_msg for {'str': 'advanced power armor'}.
#: .\at_armor.json
msgid "You sheath your %s"
msgstr "你将你的%s收鞘。"

#. ~ Use action holster_prompt for {'str': 'advanced power armor'}.
#: .\at_armor.json
msgid "Sheath knife"
msgstr "收鞘刀"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'advanced power armor'}
#: .\at_armor.json
msgid ""
"A jet black suit of very lightweight powered armor, designed to be used by "
"specialist shock troopers. Known only by the military designation 'Power "
"Armor, Advanced', it appears to have been constructed in limited quantities."
msgstr "一套乌黑、非常轻便的动力装甲，专为特种突击部队设计。仅以军用代号“先进动力装甲”为人所知，似乎产量有限。"

#: .\at_armor.json
msgid "advanced power armor helmet"
msgid_plural "advanced power armor helmets"
msgstr[0] "先进动力装甲头盔"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'advanced power armor helmet'}
#: .\at_armor.json
msgid ""
"A jet black power armor helmet designed for use with the matching suit, "
"constructed from lightweight materials, but still very protective."
msgstr "一顶乌黑的动力装甲头盔，专为配套装甲设计，采用轻质材料制成，但仍提供极佳防护。"

#: .\at_armor.json
msgid "robot helmet"
msgid_plural "robot helmets"
msgstr[0] "机器人头盔"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'robot helmet'}
#: .\at_armor.json
msgid ""
"A tough green helmet built from durable materials, designed as armor for "
"combat robots, but suitable for humans."
msgstr "一顶坚固的绿色头盔，由耐用材料制成，原为战斗机器人设计的护甲，但也适合人类使用。"

#: .\at_armor.json
msgid "steel helmet"
msgid_plural "steel helmets"
msgstr[0] "钢盔"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'steel helmet'}
#: .\at_armor.json
msgid ""
"A dull gray steel helmet with a skirt on the rear to protect against "
"shrapnel and provide extra coverage."
msgstr "一顶暗灰色钢盔，后部带有护裙，用于防御弹片并提供额外覆盖。"

#: .\at_armor.json
msgid "pilot helmet"
msgid_plural "pilot helmets"
msgstr[0] "飞行员头盔"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'pilot helmet'}
#: .\at_armor.json
msgid ""
"A thick helmet, encasing the entire head, with a large reflective visor, "
"allowing a wide field of vision."
msgstr "一顶厚重的头盔，完全包裹头部，配有大型反光面罩，提供宽阔视野。"

#: .\at_armor.json
msgid "hellfire power armor"
msgid_plural "hellfire power armors"
msgstr[0] "地狱火动力装甲"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'hellfire power armor'}
#: .\at_armor.json
msgid "A large power armor suit. It seems to be very heavily insultated."
msgstr "一套大型动力装甲。似乎具有极强的绝缘性。"

#: .\at_armor.json
msgid "hellfire power armor helmet"
msgid_plural "hellfire power armor helmets"
msgstr[0] "地狱火动力装甲头盔"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'hellfire power armor helmet'}
#: .\at_armor.json
msgid "A large power armor helmet. It seems to be very heavily insultated."
msgstr "一顶大型动力装甲头盔。似乎具有极强的绝缘性。"

#: .\at_books.json
msgid "Man or Machine"
msgid_plural "Man or Machines"
msgstr[0] "人还是机器"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'Man or Machine'}
#: .\at_books.json
msgid ""
"The first book of the \"Man or Machine\" series, focused on the electronics "
"component of robots and cyborgs. While very complex and certainly not an "
"entry-level text, it does offer many pointers and tips to even the veteran "
"programmer. Contains a few diagrams and ideas for programs that you could "
"apply to your own garage-level projects."
msgstr ""
"“人还是机器”系列的第一本书，专注于机器人与半机械人的电子元件。内容非常复杂，绝非入门读物，但即使对资深程序员也提供了许多提示与技巧。包含一些图表和程序构想，可应用于你自己的车库级项目。"

#: .\at_books.json
msgid "Man or Machine: Book Two"
msgid_plural "Man or Machine: Book Twos"
msgstr[0] "人还是机器：第二册"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'Man or Machine: Book Two'}
#: .\at_books.json
msgid ""
"The second entry in an extensively detailed series documenting the "
"construction of advanced robots and cyborgs. This book is centered on the "
"more \"hands on\" aspect of biomechanics and robots. It features many "
"different recipes, that with some enginuity, could possibly be used even in "
"a post-cataclysm enviroment."
msgstr ""
"这是一本详尽记录高级机器人与生化人建造过程的系列丛书中的第二册。本书侧重于生物力学与机器人领域中更为“实践操作”的方面。书中包含多种不同的配方，凭借一定的巧思，甚至可在灾后环境中加以运用。"

#: .\at_books.json
msgid "Man or Machine, Book Three"
msgid_plural "Man or Machine, Book Threes"
msgstr[0] "《人与机器，第三册》"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'Man or Machine, Book Three'}
#: .\at_books.json
msgid ""
"The third book in a three book series on robotics and cyborgs. This book "
"covers the biomechanic aspects, with some rather gruesome photos and "
"detailed descriptions, however, it has a wealth of knowledge, and even some "
"rudimentary designs. With some adaptations, most of the documents within "
"could be applied to your own works."
msgstr ""
"这是关于机器人学与生化人的三卷系列丛书中的第三册。本书涵盖了生物力学方面的内容，附有一些相当骇人的照片和详细描述，然而其中蕴含丰富的知识，甚至包括一些基础设计。经过适当调整，书内大部分文档均可应用于您自己的作品中。"

#: .\at_books.json
msgid "Heavy Mech Machinery"
msgid_plural "Heavy Mech Machinerys"
msgstr[0] "重型机甲机械"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'Heavy Mech Machinery'}
#: .\at_books.json
msgid ""
"A thick binder detailing the operation, maintenance and construction of "
"mechs, with much insight into the internal mechanisms."
msgstr "一本厚重的活页夹，详细阐述了机甲的操作、维护与建造，并对内部机制提供了深入见解。"

#: .\at_combustion.json
msgid "A combustion engine.  Burns fuel from a tank in the vehicle."
msgstr "一台内燃机。燃烧车辆油箱中的燃料。"

#: .\at_combustion.json
msgid ""
"A combustion engine.  Burns diesel fuel from a tank in the vehicle.  Can "
"also burn biodiesel or lamp oil, though somewhat less efficiently."
msgstr "一台内燃机。燃烧车辆油箱中的柴油燃料。也可燃烧生物柴油或灯油，但效率稍低。"

#: .\at_combustion.json
msgid ""
"An advanced combustion engine.  Burns gasoline or diesel or aviation fuel "
"from a tank in the vehicle.  Can also burn lamp oil, though somewhat less "
"efficiently.  Better power-to-weight ratio than a traditional engine, but "
"consumes more fuel."
msgstr "一台先进的内燃机。燃烧车辆油箱中的汽油、柴油或航空燃料。也可燃烧灯油，但效率稍低。相比传统发动机具有更好的功率重量比，但消耗更多燃料。"

#: .\at_containers.json
