#: .\at_melee.json
msgid "broken sniper joe"
msgid_plural "broken sniper joes"
msgstr[0] "损坏的狙击乔"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'broken sniper joe'}
#: .\at_melee.json
msgid ""
"A broken sniper joe. Much less threatening now that it lies limp on solid "
"ground. Could be gutted for parts."
msgstr "一个损坏的狙击乔。如今它瘫软在地面上，威胁性已大大降低。或许可以拆解零件。"

#: .\at_melee.json
msgid "broken met"
msgid_plural "broken mets"
msgstr[0] "损坏的机甲"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'broken met'}
#: .\at_melee.json
msgid ""
"A broken met. Much less threatening now that it lies limp on solid ground. "
"Could be gutted for parts."
msgstr "一个损坏的机甲。如今它瘫软在地面上，威胁性已大大降低。或许可以拆解零件。"

#: .\at_melee.json
msgid "destroyed cyborg"
msgid_plural "destroyed cyborgs"
msgstr[0] "被摧毁的生化人"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'destroyed cyborg'}
#: .\at_melee.json
msgid ""
"This is a heavily damaged cyborg, composed of a previously dead human, "
"several bionic upgrades, and some limiters and control systems."
msgstr "这是一个严重受损的生化人，由一具先前已死亡的人类躯体、若干生化改造部件以及一些限制器和控制系统构成。"

#: .\at_melee.json
msgid "destroyed heavy cyborg"
msgid_plural "destroyed heavy cyborgs"
msgstr[0] "被摧毁的重型生化人"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'destroyed heavy cyborg'}
#: .\at_melee.json
msgid ""
"This is a heavily damaged cyborg, sturdy in it's construction, with many "
"pieces of extra hardware attached, and a thick steel skin, covering it's "
"advanced electronics and life sustaining systems. It it's current state, "
"this cyborg is probably less man than machine."
msgstr ""
"这是一个严重受损的生化人，结构坚固，附有许多额外硬件，并覆盖着厚实的钢皮，保护其先进的电子设备和生命维持系统。以目前状态而言，这台生化人恐怕已非人类，更像是机器。"

#: .\at_melee.json
msgid "destroyed advanced cyborg"
msgid_plural "destroyed advanced cyborgs"
msgstr[0] "被摧毁的先进生化人"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'destroyed advanced cyborg'}
#: .\at_melee.json
msgid ""
"A sturdy mechanical body, with little in the way of organic matter visible. "
"It has what appears to be segments of power armor grafted to its skin and "
"steel frame, with cybernetic augmentations protruding."
msgstr "一具坚固的机械躯体，几乎看不到有机物质。其钢制骨架和外皮上似乎熔接了动力装甲的片段，并有生化增强部件突出在外。"

#: .\at_monster_drops.json
msgid "broken tribot"
msgid_plural "broken tribots"
msgstr[0] "损坏的三足机器人"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'broken tribot'}
#: .\at_monster_drops.json
msgid ""
"A broken tribot.  Now that its legs lie broken and immobile, the world seems"
" a little less threatening.  Could be gutted for parts."
msgstr "一个损坏的三足机器人。如今它的腿部断裂无法移动，世界似乎变得不那么可怕了。或许可以拆解零件。"

#: .\at_monster_drops.json
msgid "broken chickenbot"
msgid_plural "broken chickenbots"
msgstr[0] "损坏的鸡形机器人"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'broken chickenbot'}
#: .\at_monster_drops.json
msgid ""
"A broken chicken walker.  Still looks intimidating despite being permanently"
" inoperative, possibly due to the sheer size and mass.  Could be gutted for "
"parts."
msgstr "一台损坏的鸡形步行机。尽管已永久失效，但其庞大的体型和质量仍令人望而生畏。可拆解获取零件。"

#: .\at_monster_drops.json
msgid "broken tank drone"
msgid_plural "broken tank drones"
msgstr[0] "损坏的坦克无人机"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'broken tank drone'}
#: .\at_monster_drops.json
msgid ""
"A broken tank drone.  Still looks intimidating despite being permanently "
"inoperative, possibly due to the sheer size and mass.  Could be gutted for "
"parts."
msgstr "一台损坏的坦克无人机。尽管已永久失效，但其庞大的体型和质量仍令人望而生畏。可拆解获取零件。"

#: .\at_monster_drops.json
msgid "inactive tripod"
msgid_plural "inactive tripods"
msgstr[0] "未激活的三足机"

#. ~ Use action friendly_msg for {'str': 'inactive tripod'}.
#: .\at_monster_drops.json
msgid "The tribot rises to its feet and scans the area for contaminants."
msgstr "三足机器人起身并扫描区域内的污染物。"

#. ~ Use action hostile_msg for {'str': 'inactive tripod'}.
#: .\at_monster_drops.json
msgid ""
"The tribot glowers down at you and ignites its flamethrower.  Turns out you "
"hate the smell of napalm."
msgstr "三足机器人俯视着你并点燃了火焰喷射器。看来你讨厌凝固汽油的气味。"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'inactive tripod'}
#: .\at_monster_drops.json
msgid ""
"This is an inactive Honda Regnal.  Using this item involves placing it on "
"the ground, wondering how it fuels its flamethrower and turning it on.  If "
"reprogrammed and rewired successfully the tribot will then identify you as "
"an ally, roam around or follow you, and impale hostiles with its spiked "
"cable weapons."
msgstr ""
"这是一台未激活的本田Regnal。使用此物品需将其放置在地面，疑惑其火焰喷射器的燃料来源，然后启动。若成功重编程并重新接线，三足机器人会将你识别为盟友，四处巡逻或跟随你，并用其尖刺电缆武器刺穿敌人。"

#: .\at_monster_drops.json
msgid "inactive chicken walker"
msgid_plural "inactive chicken walkers"
msgstr[0] "未激活的鸡形步行机"

#. ~ Use action friendly_msg for {'str': 'inactive chicken walker'}.
#: .\at_monster_drops.json
msgid "The chicken bot rolls out and begins acquiring targets."
msgstr "鸡形机器人出动并开始锁定目标。"

#. ~ Use action hostile_msg for {'str': 'inactive chicken walker'}.
#: .\at_monster_drops.json
msgid ""
"The chicken bot swivels its turret and aims directly at you.  Don your brown"
" pants!"
msgstr "鸡形机器人旋转炮塔并直接瞄准你。快穿上你的棕色裤子！"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'inactive chicken walker'}
#: .\at_monster_drops.json
msgid ""
"This is an inactive chicken walker.  Using this item involves placing it on "
"the ground, loading the unit with the factory-loaded 5.56 rounds and 40mm "
"cartridge grenades in your inventory (if you wish to divide your ammunition,"
" set aside whatever ammunition you do NOT want to give the robot) and "
"turning it on.  If reprogrammed and rewired successfully the tank drone will"
" then identify you as a friendly, roam around or follow you, and attack all "
"enemies with a built-in firearm and grenade launcher."
msgstr ""
"这是一台未激活的鸡形步行机。使用此物品需将其放置在地面，从库存中为它装载出厂预装的5.56毫米子弹和40毫米榴弹（若想分配弹药，请先预留你不想给机器人的部分），然后启动。若成功重编程并重新接线，坦克无人机会将你识别为友方，四处巡逻或跟随你，并用内置枪械与榴弹发射器攻击所有敌人。"

#: .\at_monster_drops.json
msgid "inactive tank drone"
msgid_plural "inactive tank drones"
msgstr[0] "未激活的坦克无人机"

#. ~ Use action friendly_msg for {'str': 'inactive tank drone'}.
#: .\at_monster_drops.json
msgid "The tank drone rolls out and begins acquiring targets."
msgstr "坦克无人机出动并开始锁定目标。"

#. ~ Use action hostile_msg for {'str': 'inactive tank drone'}.
#: .\at_monster_drops.json
msgid ""
"The tank drone swivels its turret and aims directly at you.  Don your brown "
"pants!"
msgstr "坦克无人机旋转炮塔并直接瞄准你。快穿上你的棕色裤子！"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'inactive tank drone'}
#: .\at_monster_drops.json
msgid ""
"This is an inactive Beagle Mini-Tank UGV.  Using this item involves placing "
"it on the ground, loading the unit with the factory-loaded 5.56 rounds and "
"40mm cartridge grenades in your inventory (if you wish to divide your "
"ammunition, set aside whatever ammunition you do NOT want to give the robot)"
" and turning it on.  If reprogrammed and rewired successfully the tank drone"
" will then identify you as a friendly, roam around or follow you, and attack"
" all enemies with a built-in firearm and grenade launcher."
msgstr ""
"这是一台未激活的Beagle迷你坦克UGV。使用此物品需将其放置在地面，从库存中为它装载出厂预装的5.56毫米子弹和40毫米榴弹（若想分配弹药，请先预留你不想给机器人的部分），然后启动。若成功重编程并重新接线，坦克无人机会将你识别为友方，四处巡逻或跟随你，并用内置枪械与榴弹发射器攻击所有敌人。"

#: .\at_monster_drops.json
msgid "set of spidery legs"
msgid_plural "sets of spidery legs"
msgstr[0] "一组蜘蛛腿"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'set of spidery legs', 'str_pl': 'sets of spidery
#. legs'}
#: .\at_monster_drops.json
msgid "A set of big pointy legs, like the ones found under a tripod."
msgstr "一组巨大尖利的腿，类似三足机器人底部的部件。"

#: .\at_monster_drops.json
msgid "tripod chassis"
msgid_plural "tripod chassis"
msgstr[0] "三足机底盘"

#. ~ Description for {'str_sp': 'tripod chassis'}
#: .\at_monster_drops.json
msgid ""
"What's left when you remove all moving parts and electronics.  It's the "
"skeleton and armor of the tripod."
msgstr "移除所有活动部件和电子设备后的剩余部分。这是三足机器人的骨架与装甲。"

#: .\at_monster_drops.json
msgid "Pathfinder chassis"
msgid_plural "Pathfinder chassis"
msgstr[0] "探路者底盘"

#. ~ Description for {'str_sp': 'Pathfinder chassis'}
#: .\at_monster_drops.json
msgid ""
"What's left when you remove all moving parts and electronics.  It's the "
"skeleton and armor of the pathfinder."
msgstr "移除所有活动部件和电子设备后的剩余部分。这是探路者的骨架与装甲。"

#: .\at_monster_drops.json
msgid "Regulator chassis"
msgid_plural "Regulator chassis"
msgstr[0] "调节者底盘"

#. ~ Description for {'str_sp': 'Regulator chassis'}
#: .\at_monster_drops.json
msgid ""
"What's left when you remove all moving parts and electronics.  It's the "
"skeleton and armor of the Regulator tank."
msgstr "移除所有活动部件和电子设备后的剩余部分。这是调节者坦克的骨架与装甲。"

#: .\at_monsters.json
msgid "sniper joe"
msgid_plural "sniper joes"
msgstr[0] "狙击乔"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'sniper joe'}
#: .\at_monsters.json
msgid ""
"A humanoid robot, designed for combat and stealth, it is fairly well "
"armored, and quite intimidating. Rumored to be named for a young "
"revolutionary."
msgstr "一种人形机器人，专为战斗与潜行设计，装甲精良且颇具威慑力。传闻其命名源自一位年轻的革命者。"

#: .\at_monsters.json
msgid "tripod"
msgid_plural "tripods"
msgstr[0] "三足机"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'tripod'}
#: .\at_monsters.json
msgid ""
"The Honda Crop King.  Originally designed for agriculture, it has a trio of "
"spiked retractable cables and where it used to mount pesticide sprayer the "
"PrepNet Phyle have modified it to have a flamethrower for their war against "
"the Mycus."
msgstr ""
"本田Crop King。最初设计用于农业，配备三根尖刺可伸缩电缆，而PrepNet宗族将其原有的农药喷洒器改装为火焰喷射器，用于对抗真菌族。"

#: .\at_monsters.json
msgid "chicken walker"
msgid_plural "chicken walkers"
msgstr[0] "鸡形步行机"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'chicken walker'}
#: .\at_monsters.json
msgid ""
"The Northrop ATSV, a massive, heavily-armed and armored robot walking on a "
"pair of reverse-jointed legs.  Armed with a 40mm anti-vehicle grenade "
"launcher, 5.56 anti-personnel gun, and the ability to electrify itself "
"against attackers, it is an effective automated sentry, though production "
"was limited due to a legal dispute."
msgstr ""
"诺斯罗普ATSV，一种庞大、重武装且重装甲的机器人，以一对反关节腿行走。配备40毫米反车辆榴弹发射器、5.56毫米反人员枪械，并能对攻击者释放电击，是一种高效的自动哨兵，但因法律纠纷生产受限。"

#: .\at_monsters.json
msgid "Beagle Mini-Tank UGV"
msgid_plural "Beagle Mini-Tank UGVs"
msgstr[0] "比格微型坦克无人地面载具"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'Beagle Mini-Tank UGV'}
#: .\at_monsters.json
msgid ""
"The Northrop Beagle is a refrigerator-sized urban warfare UGV.  Sporting an "
"anti-tank missile launcher, 40mm grenade launcher, and numerous anti-"
"infantry weapons, it's designed for high-risk urban fighting."
msgstr "诺斯罗普·比格是一款冰箱大小的城市战无人地面载具。配备反坦克导弹发射器、40毫米榴弹发射器和多种反步兵武器，专为高风险城市战斗设计。"

#: .\at_monsters.json
msgid "met"
msgid_plural "mets"
msgstr[0] "都市执法机器人"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'met'}
#: .\at_monsters.json
msgid ""
"A human shaped robot with an empty expression on it's immobile steel face. "
"Deployed as city watchmen and riot troopers."
msgstr "人形机器人，僵硬的钢铁面孔上表情空洞。被部署为城市巡警和防暴部队。"

#: .\at_monsters.json
msgid "blob cyborg"
msgid_plural "blob cyborgs"
msgstr[0] "原生质生化人"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'blob cyborg'}
#: .\at_monsters.json
msgid ""
"An artifically made blob human, now twisted with mechanical and electronic "
"components."
msgstr "人工制造的原生质人类，现已与机械电子组件扭曲结合。"

#: .\at_monsters.json
msgid "The turret fires its smg!"
msgstr "炮塔开火了！"

#: .\at_monsters.json
msgid "heavy blob cyborg"
msgid_plural "heavy blob cyborgs"
msgstr[0] "重型原生质生化人"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'heavy blob cyborg'}
#: .\at_monsters.json
msgid ""
"An upgraded cyborg, with a better frame and more armor, it is also a cleaner"
" construction, the areas where artificial blob flesh and metal meet are less"
" patchwork, and a submachine gun mounted inside one of it's arms."
msgstr "升级版生化人，拥有更优的框架和更多装甲，结构也更精良，人造原生质肉体与金属结合处不再那么拼凑，且一只手臂内安装了冲锋枪。"

#: .\at_monsters.json
msgid "advanced blob cyborg"
msgid_plural "advanced blob cyborgs"
msgstr[0] "高级原生质生化人"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'advanced blob cyborg'}
#: .\at_monsters.json
msgid ""
"A walking mass of hardened steel, the likeness of a human ends with it's "
"face and silhouette. It's body is mostly composed of metal, with the "
"delicate artificial blob flesh components protected inside. What appears to "
"be sections of power armor are welded onto it, and a state-of-the-art "
"cerberus laser mounted on one of the arms."
msgstr ""
"行走的硬化钢块，仅面部和轮廓保留人形。身体主要由金属构成，精密的人造原生质组件被保护在内。看似动力装甲的部分焊接其上，一只手臂装备了先进的塞伯鲁斯激光器。"

#: .\at_power_armor.json
msgid "modern crusader power armor"
msgid_plural "modern crusader power armors"
msgstr[0] "现代十字军动力装甲"

#. ~ Use action msg for {'str': 'modern crusader power armor'}.
#: .\at_power_armor.json
msgid "The crusade BEGINS AGAIN."
msgstr "十字军东征再次开始。"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'modern crusader power armor'}
#: .\at_power_armor.json
msgid ""
"This armor was manufactured and was owned by a cult of basically super "
"christians and if you couldnt tell they wanted another crusade."
msgstr "这套装甲由一群基本算是超级基督徒的邪教制造并拥有，如果你没看出来，他们想要再来一次十字军东征。"

#: .\at_power_armor.json
msgid "modern crusader power armor (active)"
msgid_plural "modern crusader power armors (active)"
msgstr[0] "现代十字军动力装甲（激活）"

#. ~ Use action menu_text for {'str': 'modern crusader power armor (active)',
#. 'str_pl': 'modern crusader power armors (active)'}.
#. ~ Use action menu_text for {'str': 'modern crusader power armor helm
#. (active)', 'str_pl': 'modern crusader power armor helms (active)'}.
#: .\at_power_armor.json
msgid "Turn off"
msgstr "关闭"

#. ~ Use action msg for {'str': 'modern crusader power armor (active)',
#. 'str_pl': 'modern crusader power armors (active)'}.
#: .\at_power_armor.json
msgid "The crusade is put on hold, for now..."
msgstr "十字军东征暂时搁置……"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'modern crusader power armor (active)', 'str_pl':
#. 'modern crusader power armors (active)'}
#: .\at_power_armor.json
msgid ""
"This armor was manufactured and was owned by a cult of basically super "
"christians and if you couldnt tell they wanted another crusade.  It is "
"turned on and continually drawing power.  Use it to turn it off."
msgstr "这套装甲由一群基本算是超级基督徒的邪教制造并拥有，如果你没看出来，他们想要再来一次十字军东征。它已启动并持续消耗能量。使用以关闭。"

#: .\at_power_armor.json
msgid "modern crusader power armor helm"
msgid_plural "modern crusader power armor helms"
msgstr[0] "现代十字军动力装甲头盔"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'modern crusader power armor helm'}
#. ~ Description for {'str': 'modern crusader power armor helm (active)',
#. 'str_pl': 'modern crusader power armor helms (active)'}
#: .\at_power_armor.json
msgid ""
"While it may look like an old crusader helm complete with the cross shaped "
"opening in the front the lights in the darkness tells it is not just any "
"helm."
msgstr "虽然它看起来像一顶古老的十字军头盔，正面有十字形开口，但黑暗中闪烁的光芒表明这并非普通头盔。"

#: .\at_power_armor.json
msgid "modern crusader power armor helm (active)"
msgid_plural "modern crusader power armor helms (active)"
msgstr[0] "现代十字军动力装甲头盔（激活）"

#. ~ Use action msg for {'str': 'modern crusader power armor helm (active)',
#. 'str_pl': 'modern crusader power armor helms (active)'}.
#: .\at_power_armor.json
msgid "The %s powers down."
msgstr "%s 关闭了。"

#: .\at_professions.json
msgctxt "profession_male"
msgid "Roboticist"
msgstr "机器人专家"

#: .\at_professions.json
msgctxt "profession_female"
msgid "Roboticist"
msgstr "机器人专家"

#. ~ Profession (male Roboticist) description
#: .\at_professions.json
msgctxt "prof_desc_male"
msgid ""
"Fascinated with robots and machines since you were a child, you started a "
"small workshop, building robots for government contracts and neighborhood "
"children alike."
msgstr "自幼痴迷于机器人与机械，你开设了一家小型工作室，为政府合同和邻里孩童制造机器人。"

#. ~ Profession (female Roboticist) description
#: .\at_professions.json
msgctxt "prof_desc_female"
msgid ""
"Fascinated with robots and machines since you were a child, you started a "
"small workshop, building robots for government contracts and neighborhood "
"children alike."
msgstr "自幼痴迷于机器人与机械，你开设了一家小型工作室，为政府合同和邻里孩童制造机器人。"

#: .\at_professions.json
msgctxt "profession_male"
msgid "Biomechanist"
msgstr "生物机械师"

#: .\at_professions.json
msgctxt "profession_female"
msgid "Biomechanist"
msgstr "生物机械师"

#. ~ Profession (male Biomechanist) description
#: .\at_professions.json
msgctxt "prof_desc_male"
msgid ""
"You've always wondered what made things work, and people were no different. "
"Once you had figured out what made it tick, you wanted to improve them, and "
"what is better than sophisticated upgrades for people like strapping on a "
"fusion blaster, or implanting a cerebral booster?"
msgstr ""
"你一直好奇事物运作的原理，人类也不例外。一旦弄清了机制，你就想改进他们，还有什么比给人装上精密的升级更好呢？比如加装聚变冲击炮，或植入大脑增强器。"

#. ~ Profession (female Biomechanist) description
#: .\at_professions.json
msgctxt "prof_desc_female"
msgid ""
"You've always wondered what made things work, and people were no different. "
"Once you had figured out what made it tick, you wanted to improve them, and "
"what is better than sophisticated upgrades for people like strapping on a "
"fusion blaster, or implanting a cerebral booster?"
msgstr ""
"你一直好奇事物运作的原理，人类也不例外。一旦弄清了机制，你就想改进他们，还有什么比给人装上精密的升级更好呢？比如加装聚变冲击炮，或植入大脑增强器。"

#: .\at_professions.json
msgctxt "profession_male"
msgid "Mech Pilot"
msgstr "机甲驾驶员"

#: .\at_professions.json
msgctxt "profession_female"
msgid "Mech Pilot"
msgstr "机甲驾驶员"

#. ~ Profession (male Mech Pilot) description
#: .\at_professions.json
msgctxt "prof_desc_male"
msgid ""
"You were trained as an elite pilot, to operate the newly prototyped combat "
"mech suits, the government's response to captured Chinese intel."
msgstr "你受过精英飞行员训练，操作新原型战斗机甲套装，这是政府对获取的中国情报的回应。"

#. ~ Profession (female Mech Pilot) description
#: .\at_professions.json
msgctxt "prof_desc_female"
msgid ""
"You were trained as an elite pilot, to operate the newly prototyped combat "
"mech suits, the government's response to captured Chinese intel."
msgstr "你受过精英飞行员训练，操作新原型战斗机甲套装，这是政府对获取的中国情报的回应。"

#: .\at_rams.json
msgid ""
"A reinforced ram.  Place at the edge of vehicle to reduce damage taken in "
"collisions, and to increase damaged delivered in collisions, if the ram is "
"the first vehicle part to collide."
msgstr "加固冲撞杆。安装在车辆边缘，减少碰撞时受到的伤害，并在冲撞杆作为首个碰撞部件时增加造成的伤害。"

#: .\at_rams.json
msgid "military bullbar"
msgstr "军用防撞杆"

#: .\at_rams.json
msgid "military rambar"
msgstr "军用防撞杆"

#: .\at_ranged.json
msgid "M35-H railgun"
msgid_plural "M35-H railguns"
msgstr[0] "M35-H 轨道炮"

#: .\at_ranged.json
msgid ""
"A military developed railgun prototype, designed for mounted applications. "
"Built in decent numbers for extensive field testing. Although it was never "
"offically deployed before the cataclysm struck, it was in the process of "
"being approved. Due to high recoil, and unwieldly size, this weapon is only "
"possible to use deployed or in mounted applications."
msgstr ""
"一款军方开发的轨道炮原型，专为车载或固定式应用设计。为进行广泛的实地测试而生产了相当数量。尽管在大灾变爆发前从未正式部署，但已处于审批阶段。由于后坐力巨大且体积笨重，此武器仅能在部署或固定式应用中使用。"

#: .\at_ranged.json
msgid "USAS 20"
msgid_plural "USAS 20s"
msgstr[0] "USAS 20"

#: .\at_ranged.json
msgid ""
"The USAS 20 looks like a boxy upsized caricature of the M16A2.  Like its "
"Auto Assault-12 predecessor, it is a select-fire shotgun fed from large box "
"or drum magazines.  The in-line recoil system and sheer weight make for "
"pleasant shooting."
msgstr ""
"USAS 20 看起来像是 M16A2 的放大版方块状夸张造型。与其前身 Auto Assault-12 "
"类似，它是一款可选择射击模式的霰弹枪，使用大型弹匣或弹鼓供弹。其直列式后坐系统和巨大重量使得射击体验相当舒适。"

#: .\at_ranged.json
msgid "Desert Eagle .660"
msgid_plural "Desert Eagle .660"
msgstr[0] "沙漠之鹰 .660"

#: .\at_ranged.json
msgid ""
"One of the most recognizable handguns due to its popularity in movies and "
"video games, the Desert Eagle is better known for its menacing appearance "
"than its performance.  It's a large pistol, but its heavy weight reduces "
"recoil. This one has been manufactured and upsized to use .660 supermag."
msgstr ""
"作为电影和电子游戏中的常客，沙漠之鹰是最具辨识度的手枪之一，其威猛外观比实际性能更为出名。这是一款大型手枪，但沉重的重量有助于减少后坐力。此型号经过制造和放大，可使用"
" .660 超级马格南弹药。"

#: .\at_ranged.json
msgid "M9887"
msgid_plural "M9887s"
msgstr[0] "M9887"

#: .\at_ranged.json
msgid "What looks to be a AR-15 scaled up and bored out to use 11mm rounds."
msgstr "看起来像是 AR-15 的放大版，并扩膛以使用 11 毫米弹药。"

#: .\at_ranged.json
msgid "semi-auto"
msgstr "半自动"

#: .\at_ranged.json
msgid "burst"
msgstr "连发"

#: .\at_ranged.json
msgid "auto"
msgstr "自动"

#: .\at_ranged.json
msgid "AK50"
msgid_plural "AK50s"
msgstr[0] "AK50"

#: .\at_ranged.json
msgid ""
"One of the most recognizable assault rifles ever made, converted by some "
"youtuber to use .50 BMG."
msgstr "史上最具辨识度的突击步枪之一，被某位 YouTube 博主改装以使用 .50 BMG 弹药。"

#: .\at_ranged.json
msgid "K.O.R.D HMG"
msgid_plural "K.O.R.D HMG"
msgstr[0] "K.O.R.D 重机枪"

#: .\at_ranged.json
msgid ""
"A heavy machine gun used by the Russian military. Tends to be mounted on "
"vehicles due to its massive recoil and size. However it has a fairly low "
"weight, and given a strong enough person it could be wielded effectively "
"(unlike the M2 Browning.)"
msgstr ""
"俄罗斯军队使用的一款重机枪。由于其巨大的后坐力和尺寸，通常安装在车辆上。然而，它的重量相对较轻，若使用者足够强壮，也能有效手持使用（与 M2 "
"勃朗宁不同）。"

#: .\at_ranged.json
msgid "S M85-V1.1"
msgid_plural "S M85-V1.1"
msgstr[0] "S M85-V1.1"

#: .\at_ranged.json
msgid ""
"A hulking mass of a revolver even dwarfing the Model 500. Extremely heavy."
msgstr "一款庞大的转轮手枪，甚至比 Model 500 还要巨大。极其沉重。"

#: .\at_ranged.json
msgid "M220022a2 SPLASH"
msgid_plural "M220022a2 SPLASH"
msgstr[0] "M220022a2 溅射"

#: .\at_ranged.json
msgid ""
"A shoulder mounted ATGM system designed to replace the old disposable rocket"
" launchers, intended for use with power armor.  It has four barrels for ATGM"
" rockets."
msgstr "一款肩扛式反坦克导弹系统，旨在取代旧式一次性火箭筒，设计用于动力装甲。它配备四个反坦克导弹发射管。"

#: .\at_ranged.json
msgid "single shot"
msgstr "单发"

#: .\at_ranged.json
msgid "all barrels"
msgstr "全管齐射"

#: .\at_ranged.json
msgid "M14070a1 Bolt"
msgid_plural "M14070a1 Bolts"
msgstr[0] "M14070a1 螺栓"

#: .\at_ranged.json
msgid ""
"A military developed anti-power armor weapon mounted on the shoulder, "
"similarly to a rocket launcher. Designed for use by power armour against "
"power armour, only a few exist numbering in the hundreds. Never deployed, "
"and in perfect condition."
msgstr "一款军方开发的反动力装甲武器，类似于火箭筒，安装在肩部。设计用于动力装甲对抗动力装甲，仅存数百件，数量稀少。从未部署，且状态完美。"

#: .\at_ranged.json
msgid "duo"
msgstr "双发"

#: .\at_ranged.json
msgid "high-auto"
msgstr "高速自动"

#: .\at_ranged.json
msgid "M14083 Storm"
msgid_plural "M14083 Storms"
msgstr[0] "M14083 风暴"

#: .\at_ranged.json
msgid ""
"A military developed anti-power armor autocannon wielded only by soldiers "
"with power armor, made for shredding vehicles and people alike. Only a few "
"exist numbering in the low hundreds. Never deployed, and in perfect "
"condition."
msgstr "一款军方开发的反动力装甲自动炮，仅由穿戴动力装甲的士兵使用，用于撕裂车辆和人员。仅存数百件，数量稀少。从未部署，且状态完美。"

#: .\at_ranged.json
msgid "trio"
msgstr "三连发"

#: .\at_ranged.json
msgid "full auto"
msgstr "全自动"

#: .\at_ranged.json
msgctxt "gun_type_type"
msgid "rifle"
msgstr "步枪"

#: .\at_ranged.json
msgid "M14024a4 Hail"
msgid_plural "M14024a4 Hails"
msgstr[0] "M14024a4 冰雹"

#: .\at_ranged.json
msgid ""
"A military developed anti-infantry superheavy machine gun wielded by only "
"those with power armor, made for shredding enemy infantry en masse."
msgstr "一款军方开发的反步兵超重型机枪，仅由穿戴动力装甲者使用，用于大规模撕裂敌方步兵。"

#: .\at_ranged.json
msgid "semi"
msgstr "半自动"

#: .\at_ranged.json
msgid "low-auto"
msgstr "低自动"

#: .\at_ranged.json
msgid "M14026a1 Rend"
msgid_plural "M14026a1 Rends"
msgstr[0] "M14026a1 撕裂者"

#: .\at_ranged.json
msgid ""
"The apex of anti-infantry weapons, no ground weapon can compare to its anti-"
"infantry shredding power."
msgstr "反步兵武器的巅峰，没有任何地面武器能与之匹敌其撕裂步兵的威力。"

#: .\at_ranged.json
msgid "over-auto"
msgstr "超自动"

#: .\at_ranged.json
msgid "M14092"
msgid_plural "M14092s"
msgstr[0] "M14092"

#: .\at_ranged.json
msgid ""
"A bigass shoulder mounted cannon for mobile bunker busting. But seriously, "
"this thing is huge."
msgstr "一门巨大的肩扛式火炮，用于机动摧毁碉堡。但说真的，这东西太大了。"

#: .\at_ranged.json
msgid "M34-L railgun"
msgid_plural "M34-L railguns"
msgstr[0] "M34-L 轨道炮"

#: .\at_ranged.json
msgid ""
"A military developed railgun prototype, designed for use by infantry. Has a "
"rotating cylinder, holding twelve H&K 12mm ferromagnetic slugs."
msgstr "一款军方开发的轨道炮原型，设计供步兵使用。配备旋转弹巢，可容纳十二发H&K 12毫米铁磁弹丸。"

#: .\at_ranged.json
msgid "M26-b Gatling"
msgid_plural "M26-b Gatlings"
msgstr[0] "M26-b 加特林"

#: .\at_ranged.json
msgid ""
"A large cannon consisting of a large motor, belt feed system, and firing "
"mechanism, employing eight long barrels mounted on a rotating disc. The use "
"of eight barrels allows for high rates of fire and increased heat "
"dissipation. Firing this weapon is impossible without a mount, due to the "
"sheer size and weight."
msgstr ""
"一门大型火炮，由大型电机、弹链供弹系统和击发机构组成，采用八根长枪管安装在旋转盘上。八根枪管的使用允许高射速和增强散热。由于尺寸和重量巨大，没有支架无法发射此武器。"

#: .\at_ranged.json
msgid "semi auto"
msgstr "半自动"

#: .\at_snippets.json
msgid ""
"This is an advertisement for Wily Industries's Geologically Unstable Terrain"
" Surveyor.  It shows large robot wearing a construction hardhat preventing a"
" fallen boulder from crushing a worker."
msgstr "这是威利工业公司地质不稳定地形勘测器的广告。展示了一个戴着建筑安全帽的大型机器人，防止落石压垮工人。"

#: .\at_snippets.json
msgid ""
"This is one of the many posters printed by Wily Industries, before the "
"cataclysm. This poster features a sniper robot's green helmet, with the "
"trademark eerily glowing eye. The caption reads, in bold  \"KEEP QUIET, "
"CARELESS TALK COSTS LIVES.\""
msgstr ""
"这是威利工业公司在灾变前印制的众多海报之一。这张海报以狙击机器人的绿色头盔为特色，带有标志性的诡异发光眼睛。标题用粗体写着：“保持安静，闲谈危及生命。”"

#: .\at_snippets.json
msgid ""
"This is a poster printed by Wily Industries. This poster depicts a Met Civil"
" Protector robot, in black, red and white. The caption reads, in bold  \"WE "
"WILL KEEP YOU SAFE.\""
msgstr "这是威利工业公司印制的一张海报。这张海报描绘了一个Met民用保护者机器人，采用黑、红、白三色。标题用粗体写着：“我们将保障您的安全。”"

#: .\at_snippets.json
msgid ""
"This is a poster printed by Wily Industries. This poster depicts a Met Civil"
" Protector robot, in black, red and white. The caption reads, in bold  \"DO "
"NOT COMPROMISE YOUR SAFETY.\""
msgstr "这是威利工业公司印制的一张海报。这张海报描绘了一个Met民用保护者机器人，采用黑、红、白三色。标题用粗体写着：“切勿妥协您的安全。”"

#: .\at_snippets.json
msgid ""
"\"Those creepy-ass mets aren't as tough as the helmet robots, but they don't"
" seem to do much anyways.\""
msgstr "“那些该死的Met机器人没有头盔机器人那么硬，但它们似乎也没啥大用。”"

#: .\at_snippets.json
msgid ""
"\"I met this cyborg, pretty friendly, unlike the majority. I chatted with "
"him about various things, pretty decent, but man, what kind of messed up "
"stories he was telling me. That he saw some shit they were doing in these "
"labs long before all this mess. Creatures, not even humans, compared to him,"
" made out of blob. Yeah, artificial blob humans that just like him were "
"turned into cyborgs. What kind of shit is this? Did they know about all this"
" long before it happened? Man, it's messed up. I don't know.\""
msgstr ""
"“我遇到了一个赛博格，挺友好的，不像大多数。我和他聊了各种事情，人还不错，但天哪，他给我讲的那些破事。他说早在这一切混乱之前，就看到他们在这些实验室里搞的一些勾当。那些生物，甚至不是人类，和他相比，是用粘液造出来的。是啊，人工粘液人类，就像他一样被改造成了赛博格。这算什么事？他们是不是早就知道这一切会发生？伙计，这太乱了。我不知道。”"

#: .\at_species.json
msgid "cyborg"
msgid_plural "cyborgs"
msgstr[0] "赛博格"

#: .\at_speech.json
msgid "\"I never asked for this!\""
msgstr "“我从未要求过这个！”"

#: .\at_speech.json
msgid "\"What am I?\""
msgstr "“我是什么？”"

#: .\at_speech.json
msgid "\"Am I a human?\""
msgstr "“我是人类吗？”"

#: .\at_speech.json
msgid "\"I will serve! Oh, God!\""
msgstr "“我将效劳！哦，天哪！”"

#: .\at_speech.json
msgid "\"I was made to serve!\""
msgstr "“我被制造出来就是为了效劳！”"

#: .\at_speech.json
msgid "\"All of my systems are online.\""
msgstr "“我所有系统都在线。”"

#: .\at_speech.json
msgid "\"I'm... alive as a human?\""
msgstr "“我……像人类一样活着？”"

#: .\at_speech.json
msgid "\"Ready for combat!\""
msgstr "“准备战斗！”"

#: .\at_speech.json
msgid "\"All systems operational.\""
msgstr "“所有系统运作正常。”"

#: .\at_speech.json
msgid "\"Selective cognitive suppressant unit running at maximal efficiency.\""
msgstr "“选择性认知抑制单元以最高效率运行。”"

#: .\at_speech.json
msgid "\"Combat systems nominal.\""
msgstr "“战斗系统正常。”"

#: .\at_speech.json
msgid "\"Security program functional.\""
msgstr "“安全程序功能正常。”"

#: .\at_speech.json
msgid "\"Unit transmitter online.\""
msgstr "\"单位发射器已上线。\""

#: .\at_tools.json
msgid "robotics toolkit"
msgid_plural "robotics toolkits"
msgstr[0] "机器人工具包"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'robotics toolkit'}
#: .\at_tools.json
msgid ""
"This is a cutting-edge piece of technology: a portable, laser precision, "
"computer assisted, miniature robotics work shop. Designed to construct small"
" electronics and similar devices, it features an easy to use GUI and is "
"capable of creating sophisticated electronics and high grade robotics. May "
"also be suitable for gunsmithing."
msgstr ""
"这是一件尖端科技产品：一个便携式、激光精密、计算机辅助的微型机器人工作坊。专为制造小型电子设备及类似装置而设计，它配备了易于使用的图形用户界面，能够制造精密的电子元件和高品质的机器人。或许也适用于枪械制造。"

#: .\at_tools.json
msgid "monomolecular machete"
msgid_plural "monomolecular machetes"
msgstr[0] "单分子砍刀"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'monomolecular machete'}
#: .\at_tools.json
msgid ""
"A foot-long blade made from high-tech alloy and edged with bonded "
"nanocrystals, removed from a cyborg, and converted into a machete."
msgstr "一把一英尺长的刀刃，由高科技合金制成，边缘镶有结合纳米晶体，从赛博格身上取下，并改造成砍刀。"

#: .\at_var_vehicle_parts.json .\at_vehicle_parts.json
msgid "heavy mech leg"
msgid_plural "heavy mech legs"
msgstr[0] "重型机甲腿"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'heavy mech leg'}
#: .\at_var_vehicle_parts.json
msgid ""
"This is a heavy duty mech leg, with thick armor plating ready for the most "
"dangerous mech operations."
msgstr "这是一条重型机甲腿，配有厚重的装甲板，为最危险的机甲行动做好准备。"

#: .\at_var_vehicle_parts.json .\at_vehicle_parts.json
msgid "experimental jumbo mech leg"
msgid_plural "experimental jumbo mech legs"
msgstr[0] "实验型巨型机甲腿"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'experimental jumbo mech leg'}
#: .\at_var_vehicle_parts.json
msgid ""
"This is a impractical monstrosity that could never ever be worth its cost. "
"but thats not gonna stop you from using it."
msgstr "这是一个不切实际的怪物，其成本永远无法值回票价。但这不会阻止你使用它。"

#: .\at_var_vehicle_parts.json .\at_vehicle_parts.json
msgid "medium mech leg"
msgid_plural "medium mech legs"
msgstr[0] "中型机甲腿"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'medium mech leg'}
#: .\at_var_vehicle_parts.json
msgid ""
"This is a standard-armored mech leg, suitable for most operations not "
"requiring heavy combat armor, or a lightweight chassis."
msgstr "这是一条标准装甲的机甲腿，适用于大多数不需要重型战斗装甲或轻型底盘的操作。"

