" cant clear the path, nothing will."
msgstr "一个巨大的超级重型牛栏，用于推车和清理灌木。如果这个都清不出路来，那就没什么能清出来了。"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'extra heavy duty frame'}
#: .\at_vehicle_parts_items.json
msgid ""
"A large, sturdy frame that appears to be two heavy duty frames combined, "
"this is twice the strength, and twice the weight."
msgstr "一个大型、坚固的车架，看起来像是两个重型车架组合而成，强度加倍，重量也加倍。"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'super duty frame'}
